<h3>Added</h3>
<ul>
<li>History: record plan-utilization history for every provider with per-account names, not just Codex and Claude.</li>
<li>Menu bar: countdown timeline bar showing the time remaining until each usage limit resets.</li>
<li>Telemetry: optional self-hosted usage telemetry, configured from the About page (server URL + token) and off by default.</li>
</ul>
